            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The Kalyani School is one of the leading schools in Pune / India under the aegis of the CBSE board along with a flexible and  innovative education pedagogy I.e. linked with well known Shriram philosophy . The school provides a well rounded and holistic education across not just academics but extra curricular activities. No effort has been spared in offering excellent facilities and classrooms. Further their teachers across all subjects and extra curricular activities are deep subject matter experts and dedicated educators  who are  committed to providing the best learning experience for your child. My child looks forward to go to school every day. The management,  administration and staff are very professional and accessible.",
          "publisher": {
